{"tid":379178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵「48分鐘到廣州」廣告被轟誤導","createTime":"2017-08-29T05:54:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T04:22:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":93,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"539dc1d70a8163aaff5fe5dc879b91ea19b842a1","tid":379178,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:54:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20135668&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20135668%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170829&d=NCCDkho3GobewTXrfFF8TYsQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=c0634a14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20135668%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170829&h=e9569d39\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20135668&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170829</a><br />\n<br />\n高鐵「48分鐘到廣州」廣告被轟誤導<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n一地兩檢關注組昨日到港鐵總部抗議，斥高鐵廣告誤導。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】港鐵上周起於免費電視台播放推銷廣深港高鐵（香港段）的廣告。一地兩檢關注組昨到港鐵總部抗議，斥內容極度失實及誤導公眾，要求港鐵撤回廣告，並承諾不再使用高鐵可48分鐘到廣州作宣傳。他們亦重申政府以西九站作一地兩檢是違反《基本法》。<br />\n<br />\n促海關及立會跟進<br />\n<br />\n范國威指，廣告中有關香港直達廣州含誤導，因所謂廣州站實際是廣州南站，是位處番禺，距離廣州市中心商業區約17公里，乘客要轉乘廣州地鐵20個站才能到市中心，額外需半小時至一小時。關注組副召集人姚松炎質疑，港鐵明知直達廣州列車僅10%，90%列車中途停站，但仍指高鐵只有一地兩檢才能發揮最高效益，是誤導公眾。他促海關及立法會跟進。<br />\n<br />\n關注組將在全港設街站，提醒市民不用落實一地兩檢破壞《基本法》，也可享受高鐵效益，因深圳福田站早預留清關樓層。港鐵指，近期宣傳短片是強調高鐵的接駁及便利，短片中已列明，由西九龍站直達廣州南站只需48分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林社炳"},{"pid":"a0ca6710a7098d0d7f0524e2cf76114b9dd3ad81","tid":379178,"uid":531,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"其實到最後如果我搭過一次48分鐘去唔到，可以去海關報違反商品說明條例？"},{"pid":"250a834b1a68e6d01509a9a98c5e58e7a865c81f","tid":379178,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:55:58.000Z","msg":"先斬後奏<br />\n都起得7788重講咩<br />\n睇戲吧啦港柒"},{"pid":"8e430226e001bd31a636a3b76d10fb48cb4424e7","tid":379178,"uid":28831,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實到最後如果我搭過一次48分鐘去唔到，可以去海關報違反商品說明條例？</blockquote><br />\n然後呢?<br />\n都起完, 一地兩檢都話埋<br />\n咁佢收返收個廣告囉"},{"pid":"c9af08fb7e7c67a0513288f714127319d65048ba","tid":379178,"uid":41543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:59:59.000Z","msg":"大陸錢已袋話知你👍"},{"pid":"7e78c537fab2c418e0870ca84435fc0dc402ca6d","tid":379178,"uid":3117,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"血源詛咒五毛狗又入黎開工 想人唔反一地兩檢"},{"pid":"9caf9195ac80471ea0ef75e3e285e4f881944333","tid":379178,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸錢已袋話知你👍</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d096f05a5777367043360d555d8f6395b05641e","tid":379178,"uid":82224,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:24:09.000Z","msg":"屌番禺咁遠 不如去翻廣州東站"},{"pid":"c11cd5687bd0a6444f0aa1e41dd5081af90495e8","tid":379178,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"廣州南站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae5fdd107e287f93570d06f8554eea7b99ab7e5","tid":379178,"uid":23833,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"老老實實，根本冇乜人會搭"},{"pid":"6cbf1de2ab249d02fc54b97490c5ca8a1988ab97","tid":379178,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"廣告誤導有否觸犯商品說明條例？"},{"pid":"bf32eb3f74aeebc14ea170d77ca792f074596d2d","tid":379178,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T06:31:29.000Z","msg":"反對一地兩檢破壞基本法"},{"pid":"8b43e18bce65075e458231ed46db3aea75b45a70","tid":379178,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,